### 4. Hourly Transfer metrics
GET {{postgrestUrl}}/hourly_transfer_metrics

### 5. Hourly Transfer Volume
GET {{postgrestUrl}}/hourly_transfer_volume

### 6. TVL by Routers
GET {{postgrestUrl}}/daily_router_tvl
